## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **prostate cancer AR axis** = ADT (androgen deprivation therapy) standard, 단 castration-resistant 진입 시 AR splice variant (AR-V7) 으로 escape. quantum-VQE 의 AR-V7 / N-terminal domain targeting 가 future direction.
2. **PDE5 sildenafil 1998 paradigm** = vasoactive small-molecule, 단 cardiovascular contraindications (nitrate). quantum-VQE 의 selectivity 향상 가능.
3. **OAB β3-AR (mirabegron 2012 / vibegron 2020)** = anticholinergic 대안. 단 cardio safety + insurance access issue.
4. **BPH 5α-reductase + α1-AR combo** = standard Combo 효과적, 단 sexual side effect.
5. **bladder Ca BCG immunotherapy paradigm** = 1970s-now 의 oldest immunotherapy; molecular mechanism 미명확.
6. **interstitial cystitis** = chronic pelvic pain syndrome, mechanism 불명확. quantum 직접 X.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, urological 임상 의미 한정.

